| Config | Leaves | LR | CV Loss |
|--------|--------|-----|---------|
| baseline | 31 | 0.05 | — |
| leaves63 | 63 | 0.05 | — |
| **leaves127** | **127** | **0.05** | **0.06925** |
| leaves127_reg | 127 | 0.05 | — (regularized) |
| leaves127_lr02 | 127 | 0.02 | — |
| leaves255 | 255 | 0.05 | — |
