### Best config:
```
num_leaves: 127
learning_rate: 0.05
min_data_in_leaf: 20
max_depth: -1 (unlimited)
feature_fraction: 0.8
bagging_fraction: 0.8
bagging_freq: 5
scale_pos_weight: 0.68
num_boost_round: 3,083 (early stopping @100)
```

